{"tid":2310062,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"透過個人努力改變人生？其實有個隱藏因素比個人努力同樣重要","createTime":"2020-12-03T03:54:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T23:57:44.000Z","uid":76310,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"fd17d893989aff7ba6c764bdb6399be4e79f7b24","tid":2310062,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T03:54:50.000Z","msg":"我地睇好多新聞<br />\n都係強調透過個人努力如何改變人生<br />\n悲情城市窮苦學生，透過不斷努力成功入讀醫科生<br />\n有時睇呢d新聞多，個人都充滿熱誠和一團火<br />\n<br />\n火影都係強調主角透過不斷努力改變命運<br />\n我知<br />\n好多人會話，火影個主角根本都係出身名門望族<br />\n所以主角既努力才有效化，主角學既忍術都係上等的<br />\n其他二打六角色再努力，最多成為一打五，永遠唔夠主角玩。對方放招天照，一打五就被秒<br />\n所以好多人會話火影係名門望族的鬥爭史<br />\n<br />\n大家講既家世，家族，背景，是沒有錯。但大家都明白這是先天的，無法改變條件，大家才沒有太多討論<br />\n而且無補於事<br />\n<br />\n除左個人努力，天生既家世家族<br />\n其實仲有個隱藏既重要元素，只係太過隱藏<br />\n呢個元素，隨時比個人努力更重要<br />\n就係人生中既選擇權<br />\n<br />\n其實我地人生中有很多大大小小選擇權<br />\n中午食a b餐，這些固然無乜影響<br />\n認識什麼人<br />\n讀書讀什麼科 什麼大學 什麼工作 什麼行業 什麼公司<br />\n甚至和什麼人在一起 什麼人結婚<br />\n這些難以察覺的選擇才是影響你的人生<br />\n反而我覺得個人努力只係靠你既效率最大化<br />\n但如果選擇的是一條死路，效率最大化，又有乜用<br />\n<br />\n我講既好抽象 好9up？<br />\n試下用心想自己人生或者你知道既人的人生，做了什麼選擇，所以順其自然人生走什麼路。如果當初佢不是走呢條路，另一條路，結果又是如何呢？<br />\n<br />\n十年前<br />\n有個讀書唔太差唔太好既預科生(真係一般人既選擇)<br />\n佢可以入名牌大學水泡科或次一等大學專科<br />\n結果有人入名牌大學，有人入次一等大學<br />\n結果有人浮浮沉沉，有人做左正苦工, 有人做左專業人士上埋管理層<br />\n<br />\n有些人娶左/嫁左個衰老公/衰老婆，要離婚<br />\n其實在人生中，可能有若干個隱藏可行的選擇<br />\n只不過當事人無法去留意或理會<br />\n只係如果<br />\n原來當年中二時曾經有個學期，坐你隔一行的男/女同學，佢原來係和你/妳最配合既對象，甚至係最適合你/妳既老公/老婆<br />\n但當年無同佢交談交流<br />\n下個學年已經再無同班<br />\n他/她成為生命中的一個記不起名字的過客同學<br />\n<br />\n之前新聞話有個阿嬸，12年定13年買當刂鋪<br />\n結果跌到仆街<br />\n其實這都是人生的選擇<br />\n當年買樓等升值 已經另一回事<br />\n我知d人會話乜，事後孔明，邊個唔識<br />\n而家鬼唔知樓升左好多<br />\n所以其他隱藏選項係例如<br />\n唔一定要買樓或者當刂鋪，例如買reits收息<br />\n<br />\n當年97前，當時經濟太好，無人做正苦工<br />\n有些人貪正苦安穩，做正苦工<br />\n同時（我講梗差唔多背景，學歷，能力既人）有人做私人工，年年有人工加，仲要大把花紅<br />\n結果<br />\n正苦工果班而家做晒高層，高收入，番工做野做，做左老屎忽<br />\n有班私人工既，中年失業，結果做食蕉<br />\n我既重點唔係事後講個結果<br />\n只係想講接近相同條件下，作出既決定如何改變人生<br />\n<br />\n個人努力（努力=效率最大化）<br />\n但如果方向唔岩, 就像在森林中的小河釣魚, 和在深海中釣魚, 是完全不同的"},{"pid":"d9e57ae51db5e211650dc789203fb65b516a40ed","tid":2310062,"uid":5178,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T03:57:34.000Z","msg":"其實都係講運氣, 同有無家庭指點"},{"pid":"02b89087e9c4309f26e4fb4ec61296dd77b52c87","tid":2310062,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T08:50:50.000Z","msg":"何謂揀得啱何謂唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd179734a05c7afe72ad13e93961b3e2fef9a79","tid":2310062,"uid":60817,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:08:53.000Z","msg":"啫係選擇比努力重要"},{"pid":"929ec623b55f4939610adde91b8047572a785281","tid":2310062,"uid":56147,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T10:28:49.000Z","msg":"個人努力／選擇＋　你爸媽既個人努力／選擇<br />\n全部都係因素　　　"},{"pid":"1a842472772209468285f8735e947083487631ae","tid":2310062,"uid":229549,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T10:32:41.000Z","msg":"一命二運三風水你估流？"},{"pid":"684facbcd2a4b4d87cff5507b476f8fb44cdcd82","tid":2310062,"uid":10672,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a842472772209468285f8735e947083487631ae","tid":2310062,"uid":229549,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T10:32:41.000Z","msg":"一命二運三風水你估流？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T10:34:25.000Z","msg":"我認為一運二命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced5779f3ca2533a8ffc301e015ad2919b6489f9","tid":2310062,"uid":2679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T10:35:29.000Z","msg":"際遇好緊要 有個教授食飯果陣傾開<br />\n話廿歲時都估唔到佢依家會坐左喺到同我傾計<br />\n好多野都係行左就算 結果係點大家都控制唔到"},{"pid":"868393bc45ed1e1007913d40d37f531dae85da82","tid":2310062,"uid":100256,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T10:42:40.000Z","msg":"靠努力改變命運呢d說話係現今世代真心不合時宜<br />\n上一代人只要努力就可以買到有限既固定資產 今時今日呢d資產一早比上代人壟斷曬 下一代人普遍黎講就算點樣努力都只係為呢班上左岸既old seafood 打工 佢地根本唔會放手呢d資產 只可以講 90後 00後冇父幹就可以直接收皮 <br />\n一定有人會舉d極端成功人士做例子 我當然知道會有人靠自己努力發達 但係你做到咩？ 十萬個先一兩個only<br />\n咩疫情都唔會有得洗牌 就算洗都係洗走低下階層上流既機會"},{"pid":"ef0a52ba39ae739d7a3036e35bdb6baf57c4d9c9","tid":2310062,"uid":86204,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T10:47:36.000Z","msg":"不是要做對的選擇，而是要把選擇做對"},{"pid":"71f51acd2fcbecb0ade1ae71c123b9c63df60414","tid":2310062,"uid":125903,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T11:16:39.000Z","msg":"樂觀sir至理名言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6348404d84e758f1ea2f6e4b2c7b68a53b2ada64","tid":2310062,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"02b89087e9c4309f26e4fb4ec61296dd77b52c87","tid":2310062,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T08:50:50.000Z","msg":"何謂揀得啱何謂唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T12:32:41.000Z","msg":"08年海嘯時有人買樓，亦即係有人賣樓<br />\n<br />\n吹屎曹sir97年求佢地朋友沽貨，而佢亦沽左放租既單位，重事先聲明同條友講，將來唔好怨我"},{"pid":"2bddc388353952dde0418276e016b236e7795385","tid":2310062,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d9e57ae51db5e211650dc789203fb65b516a40ed","tid":2310062,"uid":5178,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T03:57:34.000Z","msg":"其實都係講運氣, 同有無家庭指點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T12:37:53.000Z","msg":"你覺得真係運氣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解李生係暴動時大手掃地 重比人別識李+*逃了<br />\n<br />\n點解有人海嘯時大手掃貨<br />\n<br />\n點解差唔多成績  有人揀左做engine 有人做左醫生（9x年 engine要幾條a) 之後一個中年失業 一個變左婦科聖手<br />\n<br />\n運氣only?"},{"pid":"89c781811a8e7e85b68dd74ee344e6a3b5f72a01","tid":2310062,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7fd179734a05c7afe72ad13e93961b3e2fef9a79","tid":2310062,"uid":60817,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:08:53.000Z","msg":"啫係選擇比努力重要"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T12:39:56.000Z","msg":"唔講咁遠<br />\n<br />\n揀到個好老公/老婆<br />\n一生條路已經順好多<br />\n<br />\n大把人㨂左爛既"},{"pid":"19b9de7e406772e5527562901f61fa55de841ad9","tid":2310062,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T12:40:40.000Z","msg":"其實有冇諗過在重大決定時 你為什麼做了這個決定"},{"pid":"3d2566c425d3246f48617b35096df8c1ee4df211","tid":2310062,"uid":342891,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T13:00:02.000Z","msg":"對，選擇真是很重要，<br />\n選擇入了名牌大學，要高DSE成績的科，<br />\n但搵唔到錢既人太多，<br />\n因為那些科根本冇生產力，<br />\n或者香港根本冇需求。<br />\n<br />\n求學不是求分數，<br />\n明白當然好，<br />\n不過DSE高分唔代表一個人有能力，<br />\n唔等於高分就要搵得多錢，<br />\n傻的先會覺得DSE分有價值。"},{"pid":"eb4ab03ac751942ef9e02401ce9c0cad9faf14a5","tid":2310062,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"19b9de7e406772e5527562901f61fa55de841ad9","tid":2310062,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T12:40:40.000Z","msg":"其實有冇諗過在重大決定時 你為什麼做了這個決定"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T13:15:49.000Z","msg":"樂觀SIR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為人會以當時嘅判斷去做決定<br />\n只有事後睇返先知好唔好，但你根本冇水晶球"},{"pid":"10163a789c3d8ce3c028e3bab25fa8ac96e6e338","tid":2310062,"uid":312470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T15:12:59.000Z","msg":"樓主表達能力好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咁比相同例子講同一樣野<br />\n可唔可以用一句概括左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"623946e31ebc633af5b91b36ed1598acd270945b","tid":2310062,"uid":73959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"10163a789c3d8ce3c028e3bab25fa8ac96e6e338","tid":2310062,"uid":312470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T15:12:59.000Z","msg":"樓主表達能力好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咁比相同例子講同一樣野<br />\n可唔可以用一句概括左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T16:35:00.000Z","msg":"由出世嗰時 你揀咗窮鬼老竇老母 已經-50%<br />\n然後到你讀書 入唔到名牌大學讀乞食科-25%<br />\n出嚟做嘢你揀行搵唔到錢嘅 -25%<br />\n揀咗窮嘅另一半 -100%<br />\n基本上人生巳完 及早重刷<br />\n一係你反cup搵個有能力養起你嘅另一半<br />\n咁都叫做有得救"},{"pid":"d4e15e1dddcd211548bbd72c109e4d2118061794","tid":2310062,"uid":333570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T23:57:44.000Z","msg":"選擇比努力重要<br />\n運氣加持更勝選擇<br />\n投啱胎已完勝所有"}]}